**GM** — *noting how many to place there*
> "Alright, so we'll put 3 there."

**GM** — *making a note*
> "Behind arrow slits."

**Vukradin** — *noticing Boney's position*
> "Boney's outside the gates? Oof."

**Vukradin** — *placing Boney*
> "Put him right at the door."

**Vukradin** — *on Boney's tactical role*
> "cannon fodder."

**GM** — *questioning the designation*
> "Did you guys put him as cannon fodder?"

**Vukradin** — *unapologetically*
