**[Initiative Is Rolled]**
- The DM calls for initiative; Vukradin protests briefly before accepting.

**GM** — *calling for initiative*
> "Has everybody done their thing?"

**Soma** — *surprised*
> "Oh, initiative."

**Vukradin** — *pushing back*
> "Why are we rolling initiative?"

**GM** — *responding ominously*
> "Cause we're gonna need it."

**Vukradin** — *still resisting*
> "We were just scouting…"

**Vukradin** — *firmly*
> "A role initiative when there's an actual combat. There is no bore. There is no combat. I am not rolling initiative."

**GM** — *relenting, then proceeding anyway*
> "Alright, da-da…"

