**[Initiative Order Determined]**

**Soma** — *announcing roll*
> "I got a 20."

**Vukradin** — *announcing roll*
> "I got a 22."

**Soma** — *deferring*
> "Oh, okay, then we're good."

**Vukradin** — *rolling for the Falcon*
> "Seven!"

**Vukradin** — *deadpan*
> "Good job, Falcon."

**Vukradin** — *confirming first position*
> "Okay, so I will go first. Awesome."

**GM** — *confirming Gorthok's stats and noting Falcon's HP*
