> "No, 13… The cervicals. Our class 13, hit points 15."

**GM** — *on Gorthok's presence*
> "He's got 15 and 73."

**Soma** — *surprised*
> "I didn't think we'd see Gorthok till the summoning was complete, or at least we were, you know, to the last one."

