**Vukradin** — *noting the geometry*
> "Oh, they are nicely grouped, too."

**Soma** — *appreciating the convenience*
> "Convenience."

**Vukradin** — *pleased*
> "How convenient, indeed."

**Vukradin** — *a moment later, confirming the choice*
> "30 foot cube, man."

**Vukradin** — *finalizing*
> "Guess I'll use Hypnotic Pattern."

