**[The Gate Is Blasted — Cliffhanger]**
- The DM describes the opening attack that ends the session.

**GM** — *setting up the assault*
> "From about 120 feet out, A bolt of light."

**Vukradin** — *realizing the range*
> "Range of my spell! Perfect!"

**GM** — *continuing*
> "Hold on. He… he blasts… the door. With a bolt of lightning."

**GM** — *describing the destruction*
> "The door… this door collapses. Now, the good news is none of you guys are hurt, but the gate here… I'm just gonna draw this… Has been broken."

**GM** — *describing the tactical consequence*
> "And so everybody's converging on that to attack."

**GM** — *closing the session*
> "And just to be clear, the anarchites are sort of, like, not in front this time."

**Vukradin** — *with theatrical suspense*
> "You'll have to wait until next week to find out what happens on…"

**Soma** — *playing along*
> "Oh, the suspense!"

**GM** — *confirming the cliffhanger*
> "Yes."
